# Plan gating

Plans: **free**, **pro**, **max**. Feature entitlements are defined in `src/lib/plan-features.ts` and enforced in `src/lib/plan.tsx`.

## API enforcement

```typescript
await requirePro(businessId, "featureName"); // throws PlanRequiredError
```

Handle `PlanRequiredError` in route handlers (typically HTTP 402).

## UI enforcement

Use `<ProGate businessId={…} feature="…">` for server components that hide paid UI.

## Checks

- `canUseFeature(plan, feature)` — boolean check
- `minimumPlanForFeature(feature)` — required tier
- `getBusinessPlan(businessId)` — resolves effective plan (handles expiry)

## Examples

- `aiVoiceReceptionist` — **Max only**
- `webhooks`, `reports` — **Pro+**
- `publicBookingPage` — all plans

When adding a new paid feature, update plan features, tests in `src/lib/plan.test.ts`, and admin plan config if applicable.
